# --- Rust / Cargo ---
**/target/
**/*.rs.bk

# --- Local-only data (recommended layout) ---
# Put your real `accounts.c2fa`, exports, scratch files under `local/` while developing.
/local/
**/local/

# --- Encrypted app database files (never commit real vaults) ---
*.c2fa

# --- Typical local backup exports ---
# Prefer storing exports under `/local/` (ignored above).
# These are common default names from the GUI; widen only if you need to.
**/backup-2fa.json

# --- Secrets / environment files ---
.env
.env.*
!.env.example

# --- Keys / certs (private material) ---
*.pem
*.key
*.p12
*.pfx
*.cer
*.crt
id_rsa
id_ed25519
*.ppk

# --- OS / editor noise ---
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
Desktop.ini
*.lnk

# --- Logs / temp ---
*.log
*.tmp
*.temp
*~

# --- JetBrains ---
.idea/
